Name: ECS POST INSERTION
checklistText:
<size=21>SYSTEMS & MONITORING CHECKS
ECS post insertion config</size>
GLY RSVR BYPASS vlv - OPEN
GLY RSVR OUT vlv - CLOSE
GLY RSVR IN vlv - CLOSE
PRIM GLY ACCUM QTY - 25-50%
PRIM GLY EVAP STM PRESS  - 0.09-0.14 psi

ECS RAD FLOW CONT - PWR 
PRIM GLY TO RAD vlv - NORMAL (push) 
ECS RAD HTR - PRIM 1
	ECS RAD TEMP PRIM OUT below PRIM IN
		*If outlet temp after 5 min*
		 *     above INLET TEMP*
		*PRIM FLY TO RAD vlv -
		*     BYPASS (pull)**Rechech in 10 min*
ECS RAD tb - gray 
GLY EVAP TEMP IN - AUTO 
POT H2O HTR - MNA
